There was some variability between different runs of this benchmark, the above is one of the better ones, the less good ones had performace similar to the Stream case.
Conclusions:

errorCounts(Stream) is an improvement over errorCounts(Collection).
If we're really interested in getting the best performance then we should probably drop errorCounts(Stream) and use forEach everywhere. The drawback is it's a little more verbose than the errorCounts(Stream) approach.

Thoughts?

